The paper deals with the design of a preamble for digital video broadcasting, which involves communication and information theory (cs.COMM, cs.IT), as well as network infrastructure (cs.NI) and system engineering (cs.SY). The proposed scheme also involves channel estimation, which falls under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
